snippet.title: 'I stand by my testimony': Amber Heard on Johnny Depp libel case
snippet.description:
Amber Heard says she stands by her testimony in the Johnny Depp libel case against The Sun newspaper.

Depp's ex-wife said: “It has been incredibly painful to relive the break up of my relationship, have my motives and my truth questioned, and the most traumatic and intimate details of my life with Johnny shared in court and broadcast around the world.

“I stand by my testimony and I now place my faith in British justice".
